感兴趣，而不是窗外的风景。 因此，我很想知道到底哪一种更利于孩子的心理成长？如何把握这个度？ 有位著名的教育专家说贫穷是重要的教育资源。但财富是更重要的教育资源。你如何理解这句话呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-64556378e68f10c9cf6c0728f6400cf3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446057131"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuOqd14OwhqEwEAMaCDYxNDAyNDA5IPzB1oEGMAQ48AFAMHIJNDQ2MDU3MTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1614643876.8876963", "card_id": "Q_439404517", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "22 考研网课从哪里找到?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "22 考研，但是不知道网课可以从哪里获取，"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-baa6234ac1da61c0b31e1951b564d6c6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439404517"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuOqd14OwhqEwEAMaCDU5OTIzNDkxII6lgYAGMAA4zQJAMXIJNDM5NDA0NTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}